metadata.name: The RenaiXance Rising
metadata.description: One of two digital-only covers for Vogue Singapore’s September issue, ‘The RenaiXance Rising’ was crafted by digital fashion house The Fabricant in collaboration with Singaporean fashion photographer turned 3D virtual model creator Shavonne Wong. Featuring an androgynous avatar adorned in a majestic and billowing kebaya inspired by South East Asia and the majestic costumes from the Majapahit Empire dating back to the 1300's.
